{"type": "article", "id": 19834, "title": "可以自转的宇宙飞船式森林小木屋，不能更酷炫", "description": "还可以定制你需要的型号。", "date": "2015-12-28T19:20:31Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 19098, "name": "木屋"}, {"id": 1225, "name": "美国"}, {"id": 11871, "name": "住宅"}, {"id": 21163, "name": "Solaleya"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 118, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141326JrSqjWEoxeYOcd69.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>小木屋通常用做公园里的零售商店，也有旅馆开发后作为家庭度假时的特殊体验。但这间木屋却是为家庭长住而提供的，它有 2,300 平方英尺（合约 213.7 平方米），包括厨房、餐厅、卧室（3 间）、洗手间（2.5 间）、书房等房间，非常齐全。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>法国的设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.solaleya.com/ourmodels-domespace.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Solaleya </a>修建了这间木屋，安置在了美国纽约 New Paltz 森林里。如果不仔细看，它还挺像隐藏在森林里的 UFO 或者爱斯基摩人住的冰屋，有圆形拱顶似的外形，小屋下面有一半是悬空的，有种特别的轻盈感。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141318e1E53bAJFIyoTfdS.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061413188XJanqQdcowbmU6z.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061413190hrNfMX6HoT7pUDJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141319Qpokn2wCAuxU6Feb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t木屋内部有上下两层，除了卧室和卫生间外，其余房间都是开放，它们沿着圆形的空间分布，有 360°的采光。橱柜、餐桌、洗手池等家具都使用了环形，配合着全木结构，给人温暖的家居感受。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141320m73n2qDSJ8aKYfrU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061413200TcjnQzWIMlNOX8r.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141320FiK0Z28gS9Uns1Qq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141321FZPjI2UHkt3AY8KJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061413212yz39gxXRaPtBhrb.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141322tgZiXBGR3CjJAsov.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141322I5luCXTx4Q0qUNBY.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.63703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141323j1oK6BpGfAgu2bdy.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>此外，这件小屋可以安装一个电动引擎，每 5 分钟旋转 150°。每一个角落都可以晒到太阳，也是配合光照的好办法。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141323eag0YNtKLoQWThpM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75246132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这间木屋正在美国房地产搜索网站 <a href=\"http://www.estately.com/listings/info/116-canaan-road\" target=\"_blank\">estately </a>上挂牌出售，售价 89.9 万美元。网站上还贴出了周围上学很方便的宣传语。如果只愿住一周度假，需要 2300 美元。另外，修建圆形木屋的 </span>Solaleya 还提供不同型号的木屋定制服务，<a href=\"http://www.solaleya.com/ourmodels-domespace.htm\" target=\"_blank\">这里是工作室的链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141324LB4Xx7KfSRpWTyAz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56256572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141324JAWNK7djeLQmSGsH.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56256572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606141325HdLYOD91IGTRmMQl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56256572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061413250vfYH6WSLMB8ZXa1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56256572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.estately.com/listings/info/116-canaan-road\" target=\"_blank\">estately</a></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}